Description: Swagger API Documentation builder for aiohttp server
 aiohttp-swagger is a library that allows you to easily add Swagger
 documentation to your aiohttp web server applications. It provides
 decorators and utilities to automatically generate API documentation
 from your route handlers and data models.
 .
 This package provides automatic Swagger/OpenAPI documentation generation
 for aiohttp-based web applications, making it easier to document and
 test REST APIs.
